Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.43,0:27:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 国防部想出马抓获病毒 但我相信用不着他们出手\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, the pentagon's furious to have the plague captured but I'm sure we don't have to play that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.83,0:27:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们反恐局的仨个头儿 又在秘密行动\N{\r原文字幕}Now this operation again is a secret between 3 CTU agents
