Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.53,0:27:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你打电话来只是为了训斥我 那太不合时宜了\N{\r原文字幕}But if you're just calling to reprimand me, you're doing this both undeserved.
