Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.48,0:27:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个行动 规模有多大?\N{\r原文字幕}This operation, how large is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.43,0:27:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们派了十几个特种部队队员 把守在周边待命准备行动\N{\r原文字幕}We've had a dozen of delta teams in the area waiting for the signal to go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.73,0:27:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人手够吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Will that be sufficient?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.03,0:28:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能这些人\N{\r原文字幕}It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.23,0:28:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多派人的话 很容易被发现\N{\r原文字幕}Any more bodies down there, we're rather being spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.33,0:28:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我到底会发生什么?\N{\r原文字幕}Tell me exactly what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.08,0:28:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有这个时间了 先生\N{\r原文字幕}We don't have time for this, sir.
