Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.88,0:28:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们非常肯定我们已经做好准备\N{\r原文字幕}We're pretty sure we've our bases covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.76,0:28:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常肯定也不够好\N{\r原文字幕}Pretty sure isn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.92,0:28:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要确保万无一失\N{\r原文字幕}You make this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.64,0:28:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 先生\N{\r原文字幕}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.77,0:28:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们开始\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, we're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.13,0:28:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔡斯 进展如何?\N{\r原文字幕}Chase, what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.23,0:28:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来他们要完成确认了\N{\r原文字幕}It looks like they're about to get confirmation.
