Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.84,0:36:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用放弃任何东西\N{\r原文字幕}without having to give everything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.74,0:36:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太荒谬了\N{\r原文字幕}This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.24,0:36:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你了解我 朱莉娅\N{\r原文字幕}You know me, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.74,0:36:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我说我要怎样的时候\N{\r原文字幕}When I say I can make something happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.54,0:36:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好相信我能做到\N{\r原文字幕}you better believe I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.84,0:36:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么做?\N{\r原文字幕}How would you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.44,0:36:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 我们要私下见个面\N{\r原文字幕}First of all, we need to meet in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.24,0:36:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候?\N{\r原文字幕}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.24,0:36:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须现在\N{\r原文字幕}Has to be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.94,0:36:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能晚上这个时候出去还不引起艾伦的怀疑\N{\r原文字幕}I can't leave this house at this time of night without Alan wondering what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.24,0:36:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去找你\N{\r原文字幕}Then I'm coming to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.44,0:36:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克 别开枪\N{\r原文字幕}Jack, hold your fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.24,0:36:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔡斯?\N{\r原文字幕}Chase?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.39,0:36:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.54,0:36:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?\N{\r原文字幕}You're alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.29,0:36:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我没事\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, I'm alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.04,0:36:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病毒是首要任务\N{\r原文字幕}Our first priority is the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.54,0:36:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆是第二位的\N{\r原文字幕}Ramon is our second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.54,0:36:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论谁看到他都不准开枪\N{\r原文字幕}Anybody gets a visual, standing order is do not fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.94,0:36:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Are we clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.74,0:36:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\r原文字幕}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.44,0:36:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来他从这条路跑了 但如果我是他我会朝北跑\N{\r原文字幕}Looks like he's coming down the path. But if I were him, I'd headed north.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.34,0:37:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝北会遇到一条河\N{\r原文字幕}Heading north would run into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.24,0:37:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉直升机我们的坐标 让他们河上汇合\N{\r原文字幕}Give the chopper our coordinates. Tell them to converge on the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.34,0:37:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再派一对人回到那条路以防他往回跑\N{\r原文字幕}Send another team back down the path in case he doubles back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.09,0:37:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们4个去那条路 另外2个跟我来\N{\r原文字幕}We want 4 of you down that path, and I want 2 of you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.84,0:37:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走\N{\r原文字幕}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.14,0:37:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆拿着病毒向北方位置453.6逃去\N{\r原文字幕}Ramon's in possession of the virus, he's headed north position 453.6.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.74,0:37:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到 453.6\N{\r原文字幕}Roger, 453.6
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.25,0:37:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都结束了 拉姆\N{\r原文字幕}It's over, Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.25,0:37:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你无路可逃了\N{\r原文字幕}There's nowhere else for you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.25,0:37:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会回监狱的\N{\r原文字幕}I'm not going back to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.15,0:37:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个我们之后再谈\N{\r原文字幕}After we settling down, we'll talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.65,0:37:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}Stop, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.75,0:37:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好谈的\N{\r原文字幕}There's nothing to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.59,0:37:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把病毒放下\N{\r原文字幕}Put the cylinder down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.96,0:37:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想朝你开枪 快把病毒放下\N{\r原文字幕}I don't wanna have to shoot you, just put the cylinder down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.16,0:37:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克 下命令吧\N{\r原文字幕}Jack, say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.25,0:37:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不到时候\N{\r原文字幕}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.88,0:37:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙...\N{\r原文字幕}Ramon...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.75,0:38:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有特权能够帮你减刑\N{\r原文字幕}I have the authority to cut a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.35,0:38:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是要病毒\N{\r原文字幕}All we want is the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.15,0:38:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把病毒慢慢放下吧\N{\r原文字幕}Just put the cylinder down slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.62,0:38:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 我不想朝你开枪\N{\r原文字幕}Please, I don't wanna shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.25,0:38:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来\N{\r原文字幕}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.05,0:38:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢轻轻地把它放地上\N{\r原文字幕}Put it on the ground nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.05,0:38:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\r原文字幕}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.15,0:38:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下!\N{\r原文字幕}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.75,0:38:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-蔡斯 你没事吧?  -嗯\N{\r原文字幕}-Chase, are you alright?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.75,0:38:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你电话给我\N{\r原文字幕}Give me your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.55,0:38:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是杰克·鲍尔 让我跟阿尔梅达讲话\N{\r原文字幕}This is Jack Bauer. Pass me through to Almeida now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.55,0:39:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上\N{\r原文字幕}Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.75,0:39:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么了 杰克?  -我们没拿到病毒\N{\r原文字幕}-What's going on, Jack?  -We do not have the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.45,0:39:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复 我们没拿到病毒\N{\r原文字幕}I repeat, we do not have the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.55,0:39:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆拿到的病毒罐是炸弹\N{\r原文字幕}The cylinder Ramon was carrying was ripped with a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.35,0:39:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿马多尔肯定调包了 我们能找到他吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Amador must have switched it, do we have a position on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.95,0:39:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特种部队在跟着他呢 他跑不远的\N{\r原文字幕}Delta's on with him. He won't get far.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.65,0:39:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是阿马多尔的计划 他已经安排好了逃跑路线\N{\r原文字幕}It must be Amador's original plan which he sees as rearranged escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.15,0:39:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提醒特种部队\N{\r原文字幕}please advise delta team.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.40,0:39:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在做呢 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}We're on it, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.65,0:39:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 尼娜·迈尔斯也跑了\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, Nina Myers' out there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.05,0:39:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她跟这个有关吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Any chance she was involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.45,0:39:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 炸弹就是给她的\N{\r原文字幕}No, the bomb was made for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.95,0:39:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特种部队在你以西2公里处截下了阿马多尔 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}Delta has Amador pinned 2 kms west of you, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.05,0:39:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到 我们就过去\N{\r原文字幕}Copy that, we're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.10,0:39:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔡斯 让你的人做好准备\N{\r原文字幕}Chase, get your team ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.15,0:39:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向西2公里 沿着公路\N{\r原文字幕}2 kms to west, stick with the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.45,0:39:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特种部队3队...\N{\r原文字幕}Up delta 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.25,0:40:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下车 快!\N{\r原文字幕}Get out of the vehicle, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.55,0:40:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,举起手来\N{\r原文字幕}Hands in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.75,0:40:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动一下 你就死定了\N{\r原文字幕}Move a muscle, you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.75,0:40:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地趴在地上\N{\r原文字幕}Very slowly, get on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.65,0:40:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上!\N{\r原文字幕}Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.25,0:41:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走\N{\r原文字幕}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.05,0:41:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼...\N{\r原文字幕}Tony...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.95,0:42:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特种部队遭到埋伏全部牺牲了\N{\r原文字幕}The delta team has been taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.75,0:42:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿马多尔跑掉了\N{\r原文字幕}Amador's escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.05,0:42:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 阿马多尔的手机完全失去信号了\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, Amador's cell phone just went completely dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.05,0:42:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克.\N{\r原文字幕}Jack
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.85,0:42:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克 说话\N{\r原文字幕}Jack, come in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.40,0:42:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我是鲍尔\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, it's Bauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.95,0:42:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿马多尔伏击了特种部队3队 重复 阿马多尔伏击了特种部队3队\N{\r原文字幕}Amador ambushed delta 3, I repeat Amador ambushed delta 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.95,0:42:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个圈套\N{\r原文字幕}It was a set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.35,0:42:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能追踪到位置吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Do you have a position?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.65,0:42:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能 我们用手机信号追踪的\N{\r原文字幕}Negative, we're tracking by cell phone signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.95,0:42:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伏击开始时我们就失去信号了\N{\r原文字幕}We lost it when the ambush happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.35,0:42:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卫星呢?\N{\r原文字幕}What about satellite?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.35,0:42:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 现在没有可视卫星覆盖这个区域\N{\r原文字幕}No, there's no visual satellite coverage of this area at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.95,0:42:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 收到\N{\r原文字幕}Son of a bitch. Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.75,0:42:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特种部队3队都牺牲了\N{\r原文字幕}Delta 3's been taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.55,0:42:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们追踪不到阿马多尔了\N{\r原文字幕}They don't have a position on Amador.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.65,0:42:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么做?\N{\r原文字幕}what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.95,0:42:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须找到尼娜\N{\r原文字幕}We've got to find Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.25,0:42:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带你的人去高地 我在这掩护你们\N{\r原文字幕}Take your team up to the high ground. I'll cover you down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.85,0:42:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 你们 跟我来\N{\r原文字幕}Okay. You guys, come on. We'll find...
